original: Ernås, Ragnar Sven Albin, komminister, Ekbyvall, f. 2/6/08 i Gbg. G. 35 m. org. Britta Mårtensson. Barn: Kerstin f. 36, Anna-Stina 38, Margareta o. Sven Ragnar ff. 42. ■— S’tud:-ex. i Gbg 28, teol. kand. samt prakt, teoil. prov 32, prästv. f. Skara -stift 33. Tjg. i Mariestad o. Fägre, kommin. i Ekby sed. 36, red :’sekr. f. Skara stift i ord o. bild.
translated: Ernås, Ragnar Sven Albin, vicar, Ekbyvall, born on June 2, 1908 in Gothenburg. Married in 1935 to Britta Mårtensson. Children: Kerstin born in 1936, Anna-Stina born in 1938, Margareta and Sven Ragnar born in 1942. Completed undergraduate studies in Gothenburg in 1928, theology degree and practical theological examination in 1932, ordained as a priest for the Diocese of Skara in 1933. Working in Mariestad and Fägre, and serving as a vicar in Ekby since 1936. Also served as secretary of Skara Diocese in word and image.
